{"tid":2166221,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[震驚 !!! 突發 !!!] 列斯聯 決定球會將改名成 馬列斯聯 !!!!","createTime":"2020-08-20T09:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T15:45:55.000Z","uid":124655,"like":3,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf0af652e3e21975dd29d185c8b866eae2536ee","tid":2166221,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:51:30.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】英超升班<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">馬列斯聯</span></strong></span>周三推出新球季新戰衣，有球迷投訴贊助商logo太大。<br />\n<br />\n闊別頂級聯賽16年的列斯聯，將在新球季再次重返英超戰場，周三會方正式推出主場戰衣，深得網民的好評。這件戰衣是列斯聯首次跟adidas合作，雙方此前簽下5年合約，且看能否見證又一個列斯聯王朝？<br />\n<br />\n該設計依然用上傳統的白色，除了會徽外，還有約克郡徽章，盡顯球隊的本土情懷。不過，有網友反映球衣少了黃色元素，如果肩上黑色三間換成黃色就更佳，不過不少人均表示一定會購買。<br />\n<br />\n至於胸口贊助商則令人有點失望，該贊助商是來自菲律賓的網上賭博網站，該網站之前捲入過英超和保加利亞的假波醜聞。Luke Hulley留言道：「很好看的戰衣，只是贊助商的logo看上去太大。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/2/942/30483931942/30496011353_600x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F2%2F942%2F30483931942%2F30496011353_600x390.jpg&h=ae960690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nlin: <a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=30483931942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D30483931942&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5QoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=f53d27a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=30483931942</a>"},{"pid":"f47420b2365dbaa1e84ffdc040dc7c65fae35b77","tid":2166221,"uid":11381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:54:10.000Z","msg":".."},{"pid":"bd0c63ef072a5f38ff284cf545c2af4abb81908e","tid":2166221,"uid":46904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:54:50.000Z","msg":"做咩姐你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405476c9b8a253e22d8abba46085824b8f784b48","tid":2166221,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply